Title: Clesse Compac TR800 OPSO 2cyl ACO Kit
Description: Telemetry-ready, this Clesse CompacTR800 OPSO two-cylinder LPG automatic changeover regulator kit is compatible with the electronic CompacTi device, allowing for remote cylinder readings and notifications. The CompacTR800 includes a push-to-set over-pressure safety system with inbuilt indication and is supplied with pigtails, an ECV and safety plaque.
category: Heating/Flue & Chimney Systems/Flue Terminals/Flue Terminals.csv -> Clesse Compac TR800 OPSO 2cyl ACO Kit
Feature 1: Telemetry ready to accept CompacTi remote electronic cylinder monitoring device.
Feature 2: Excellent change-over performance, further enhanced by the CompacTi device when fitted using Clesse Integrated Intelligence to delay notification on the CompacTi application until all gas is used on one side.
Feature 3: OPSO “Push to Set” Consumer safety system with indication
Feature 4: “le Clic” changeover head position with reserve indicator
Feature 6: Non return valves and filters on both Inlet ports to prevent leakage when changing cylinders
Feature 7: Equipped with a limited flow safety relief valve (LRV)
Feature 8: Protected breather vents positioned under the tough plastic ABS Weather proof designed casing

Description: It may be tempting to opt for a low cost spare part, but do consider the impact that this may have. Counterfeit parts are typically substandard, manufactured from poor quality materials thus impacting on the design and strength of the product.
